    <description>The flow accepts an input Employee and a Date. It then finds all Attendance from the date onwards on the Employee, finds the Work Schedules and uses them to update existing Attendance. The flow is called from the &quot;SF - Create Work Schedule&quot; screenflow and is used to update future attendance, once an Employee&apos;s Work Schedule changes.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
